:'''Lila:''' Ahh, I do have something I want help with...
:'''Lila:''' Previously, I asked some Silvermane Guards I knew to help me look for traces of wild animals when they go out on patrol.
:'''Lila:''' It has been a long time since then, and I haven't received any news from them... until now.
:'''Lila:''' An excited Guard told me a few days ago that he saw activities of direwolves on the Southern Snow Plains &mdash; That's big news!
:'''Lila:''' But I really don't want to keep asking the Guards to help me collect traces of wild animals... Their own job is difficult enough as it is.
:'''Lila:''' I can tell that you have a lot of experience adventuring, right? If possible... Could I ask you to head to the outlying Snow Plains and find traces of wild animals?
:'''Lila:''' Fur, paw marks, and even excrement are okay! Please! I will definitely repay you with rich rewards!
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
