::'''Lila:''' You sure are quick! Thank you, that should be perfect. I just finished writing my reply letter as well. Please give it to my father the next time you go see him.
::'''Lila:''' He's always been quite stubborn and too hard on himself. I can tell that the things he wrote about in the letter aren't really what he has done.
::'''Lila:''' Ever since I can remember, he always liked to act like a hero in front of me and exaggerate things... He probably thinks that if he doesn't achieve something big in the Silvermane Guards, he will be a shame to the family.
::'''Lila:''' But I've never cared about that. He's always worked hard to give me a better life, better than most... That's already enough for me to be truly grateful for him.
::'''Lila:''' Argh, sorry for going on about our family matters. Anyway... I just hope that my father can return home safely.
