:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::'''Lila:''' I've been doing alright. I just haven't been sleeping so well.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Did something happen?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023668-->
:::'''Lila:''' Oh... I'm worried you'll laugh if I tell you. I am a member of an exploratory vanguard dispatched by the Town Hall to go outside Belobog. I'm responsible for investigating unknown flora and fauna.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So the reason you aren't sleeping is that you want to imitate owls?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023670-->
:::'''Lila:''' Owls? What's an owl? Never heard of it... Is there a creature like that outside these walls? If there really is such an animal, then I must to go and do some research.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501023672-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023672-->
::'''Lila:''' Ah... You probably don't know, right? The Town Hall recently arranged for some people to explore the area outside the city. Supposedly, the Underworld will be returning to normal soon. Pretty soon, everyone will be able to come and go as they please.
::'''Lila:''' The Town Hall gave me some outdoor gear. Once my preparations are complete, I'll go and investigate the habitat of the wild flora and fauna out there. I'm going to record them to make a manual.
::'''Lila:''' So, whenever I think about how my research has a chance of achieving a major breakthrough, I get so excited that I can't sleep a wink...
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
